    "description": {
      "value": "<div><hr /><div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>You are an able physician, allowing you to mend wounds quickly and get your allies back in the fight. You gain the following benefits:</p><ul class=\"rd__list\"><li class=\"rd__li \">When you use a @item[healer's kit|phb] to stabilize a dying creature, that creature also regains 1 hit point.</li><li class=\"rd__li \">As an action, you can spend one use of a @item[healer's kit|phb] to tend to a creature and restore [[/r 1d6 + 4]] hit points to it, plus additional hit points equal to the creature's maximum number of Hit Dice. The creature can't regain hit points from this feat again until it finishes a short or long rest.</li></ul></div>\n\t\t\t</div></div>",
